Rajiv and Vinod are best friends Rajeev give set of in integers Vinod has to divide the set in two subsets of N by 2 sizes in each such that the difference of the sum of two subsets is as minimum as possible if NSK even the sizes of the two subset must be strictly and by two and if n is odd the size of one subject might must be and minus one by two and size of the Other subset must be and plus one by two.

